    "RunResultStreaming extends RunResultBase (inheritance)",
    "AgentHookContext extends RunContextWrapper (inheritance)",
    "RunResultBase contains RunContextWrapper (composition via context_wrapper)",
    "RunResultBase contains list[RunItem] (composition via new_items)",
    "RunResultBase contains list[ModelResponse] (composition via raw_responses)",
    "RunResult contains list[ToolApprovalItem] (composition via interruptions)",
    "RunResultStreaming contains list[ToolApprovalItem] (composition via interruptions)",
    "RunResult.to_state() creates RunState",
    "RunResultStreaming.to_state() creates RunState",
    "RunState contains RunContextWrapper (composition via _context)",
    "RunState contains list[RunItem] (composition via _generated_items, _session_items)",
    "RunState contains list[ModelResponse] (composition via _model_responses)",
    "RunState.approve/reject delegates to RunContextWrapper.approve_tool/reject_tool",
    "RunContextWrapper contains _ApprovalRecord (composition via _approvals dict)",
    "RunContextWrapper contains Usage (composition)",
    "RunConfig contains ModelSettings (dependency)",
    "RunConfig contains TracingConfig (dependency)",
    "RunConfig contains SandboxRunConfig (composition)",
    "RunConfig contains list[InputGuardrail] (dependency)",
    "RunConfig contains list[OutputGuardrail] (dependency)",
    "SandboxRunConfig contains SandboxConcurrencyLimits (composition)",
    "CallModelData contains ModelInputData (composition)",
    "CallModelData references Agent[TContext]",
    "ToolErrorFormatterArgs references RunContextWrapper[TContext]",
    "RunResultBase.agent_tool_invocation returns AgentToolInvocation | None",
    "AgentRunner.run() uses RunConfig, RunHooks, RunErrorHandlers, Session",
    "RunState._current_step is NextStepInterruption | None"
  ],

  "key_flows": [
    "Fresh run: Runner.run(agent, str/list) → AgentRunner.run() → create RunConfig, RunContextWrapper → agent loop (call LLM, tool calls, handoffs) → return RunResult",
    "Resume run: Runner.run(agent, RunState) → AgentRunner.run() → detect is_resumed_state → resolve context/settings from RunState → resume agent loop → return RunResult",
    "Streaming: Runner.run_streamed(agent, input) → AgentRunner.run_streamed() → create RunResultStreaming with asyncio.Task (run_loop_task) → return immediately → caller consumes stream_events() async iterator",
    "Interruption/HITL: run produces RunResult with interruptions → result.to_state() → RunState.approve/reject → Runner.run(agent, state) to resume",
    "Cancellation: RunResultStreaming.cancel(mode) → immediate (cancel tasks, drain queues) or after_turn (soft flag, loop checks and stops before next turn)"
  ],

  "constants_and_types": [
    "DEFAULT_MAX_TURNS = 10",
    "CURRENT_SCHEMA_VERSION = '1.9' (RunState serialization)",
    "ReasoningItemIdPolicy = Literal['preserve', 'omit']",
    "ToInputListMode = Literal['preserve_all', 'normalized']",
    "CallModelInputFilter = Callable[[CallModelData], MaybeAwaitable[ModelInputData]]",
    "ToolErrorFormatter = Callable[[ToolErrorFormatterArgs], MaybeAwaitable[str | None]]",
    "TContext = TypeVar (default=Any)"
  ],

  "important_notes": [
    "Runner is a pure static facade over AgentRunner; AgentRunner is experimental/internal.",
    "RunResultBase is abstract (ABC); concrete subclasses are RunResult (non-streaming) and RunResultStreaming.",
    "RunState is the durable pause/resume boundary — carries full snapshot for HITL flows, serializable via to_json()/from_json().",
    "RunContextWrapper wraps user context + approval state + usage; NOT sent to LLM.",
    "AgentHookContext extends RunContextWrapper and is passed to agent lifecycle hooks.",
    "RunResultStreaming holds asyncio Queues and Tasks; stream_events() is an async iterator.",
    "Both RunResult and RunResultStreaming expose to_state() which creates RunState for resume.",
    "Conversation continuity: 4 strategies — to_input_list(), Session, conversation_id (server), previous_response_id (server).",
    "call_model_input_filter in RunConfig hooks right before each model call to shape input.",
    "interruptions list on results holds ToolApprovalItem objects pending human approval."
  ]
}
